metadata.description:
over the next 6 weeks Clear Eyes and i will be creating a project.

this is the first installment of ‘dialogue’.  Clear Eyes will make a song directly in response to this song, sampling elements of it in the process. i will then make a song directly in response to that song, sampling elements of it in the process.

we will go back and forth this way until we have 6 songs.

1 song each week.

each song is made in real-time, in dialogue with the song that came before it.

this is DIALOGUE.
